[C]Was the grandest place on [G]earth
[A7]Till I roamed around from town to town
[D7]Now I know what it's worth
[G]Listen while I'll tell you bout the place I [C]mean
[G]It's my little ole home [D7]down in New [G]Orleans
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 2}
