[A7]That's where I long to [D7]be
[G]In the Dixie land where the white cotton [C]grows
[A7]Is calling now to [D7]me
[G]And soon I'll be in the land of my [C]dreams
[G]That's my little ole home [D7]down in New [G]Orleans
{end_of_verse}

